          "id": "welcome",
          "kind": "builtin:markdown",
          "title": "Which regions grew fastest last quarter?",
          "grid": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "w": 12, "h": 6 },
          "collapsed": false,
          "hidden": false,
          "props": {
            "markdown": "# Which regions grew fastest last quarter?\n\n**agent:growth** · answered 4h ago · sourced from `revenue.q3.by_region`\n\nAPAC led growth at **+34% QoQ**, driven by a partner-channel push in Singapore and Tokyo enterprise renewals. EMEA held steady on renewal strength; LATAM's dip traces to a single churned logo (Nubank-adjacent fintech, now recovered on a smaller plan).\n\n| Region | QoQ Growth | Net New MRR |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| APAC | +34% | $18,200 |\n| NA | +11% | $22,900 |\n| EMEA | +9% | $14,050 |\n| LATAM | -4% | -$2,100 |\n\nThis whole dashboard is one JSON document — **any AI can build it, any human can edit it.**\n\n- Click **🤖 simulate agent** above to watch an agent compose a new view live.\n- Drag widgets, resize them, or hit *undo* — you're editing the same document the agent uses.\n- Approve (or reject) any agent-authored widget before it ever runs — sandboxed, by construction.\n\nAsk something below to see the action-form pattern in action."
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "ask-agent",
          "kind": "builtin:action-form",
          "title": "Ask the Agent",
          "grid": { "x": 0, "y": 6, "w": 6, "h": 6 },
          "collapsed": false,
          "hidden": false,
          "props": {
            "template": "Draft a {tone} summary about {topic}.",
