          "id": "postmortem",
          "kind": "builtin:markdown",
          "title": "Post-mortem: INC-233",
          "grid": { "x": 0, "y": 6, "w": 12, "h": 5 },
          "collapsed": false,
          "hidden": false,
          "props": {
            "markdown": "## INC-233 — Approval queue backlog\n\n**Severity:** sev1 · **Duration:** 26m · **Impact:** 340 pending-review runs delayed\n\n**Root cause:** the outbound webhook delivering `dashboard.widget.approve` notifications lost its connection to the queue broker; retries backed off silently instead of alerting, so the approval UI looked healthy while the backlog grew.\n\n**Fix:** added a dead-letter alert on the webhook retry path and a queue-depth stat card to Fleet so backlog growth is visible before it pages anyone.\n\n**Follow-ups:** (1) webhook health check every 60s, (2) queue-depth alert threshold at 25, (3) runbook link added to on-call rotation."
          }
        }
      ]
